==English==
===Noun===
'''Bible-basher''' (''plural'' '''Bible-bashers''')
# {{UK}} {{perjorative}} A [[fundamentalist]] [[Christian]] [[preacher]], who is seen to take every opportunity to talk about Christianity and convert those around them, especially against the other peoples' wills.
#: ''I don't ever go to my local church any more, it's become filled with stupid, [[new-age]] '''bible bashers'''...''
# {{US}} A person who tries to find fault with the [[Bible]], [[Christianity]] or Christian teaching.

